    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场支持 2-4 名玩家的史诗级雪球大战，支持线上与本地多人模式！ <br>滚大你的雪球，利用各种强化道具把朋友们击飞吧！<br>你准备好开战了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>趣味战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“雪球来啦——！！”</strong><br>扔出你的雪球，把对手击倒！<br>但千万别投空了，没有雪球的你非常脆弱！ </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/d89ad1255cd358355895c181ede4cf7c.poster.avif?t=1752049983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/d89ad1255cd358355895c181ede4cf7c.webm?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/d89ad1255cd358355895c181ede4cf7c.mp4?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全力冲刺！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和朋友来一场正面较量，像一只倔强的山羊一样猛撞！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/2ae42ab9d957ccf615059e9738b1b8ef.poster.avif?t=1752049983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/2ae42ab9d957ccf615059e9738b1b8ef.webm?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/2ae42ab9d957ccf615059e9738b1b8ef.mp4?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与地图互动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图是你取得优势的利器。善加利用，给你的朋友一个惊喜吧！ </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/72666a48e0b7ec500509fe5005822e2c.poster.avif?t=1752049983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/72666a48e0b7ec500509fe5005822e2c.webm?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/72666a48e0b7ec500509fe5005822e2c.mp4?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >传送门！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用地图上的传送门，在对手防不胜防的时候偷袭他们！（你试过把雪球扔进传送门吗？）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/011c296680e172ae4a45f4deb335b9b0.poster.avif?t=1752049983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/011c296680e172ae4a45f4deb335b9b0.webm?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/011c296680e172ae4a45f4deb335b9b0.mp4?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“动物迈出一步，却从移动的方块上跌落，你以为那是我吗？不，是我敲响了钟声。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >—— 海鹦皇帝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/aa3e1a009f0754defe77f0c15c5fae64.poster.avif?t=1752049983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/aa3e1a009f0754defe77f0c15c5fae64.webm?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/aa3e1a009f0754defe77f0c15c5fae64.mp4?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最重要的是</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了享受游戏的乐趣，向你的朋友们展示你才是最强的玩家！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/8c43c42b09366a22f7bf51ab44f735bf.poster.avif?t=1752049983\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/8c43c42b09366a22f7bf51ab44f735bf.webm?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247510/extras/8c43c42b09366a22f7bf51ab44f735bf.mp4?t=1752049983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
